{"tid":28291,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"（亞洲男神）木村拓哉算唔算好男人","createTime":"2016-12-07T23:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T02:18:14.000Z","uid":22643,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc3b8f96d9b5399a04bbd2a1b356756bfd326272","tid":28291,"uid":22643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T23:48:58.000Z","msg":"身為全日本最靚仔最紅嘅男人<br />\n係最高峰時期唔理自己前途<br />\n要向外界宣布結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多年都好保護家庭<br />\n興趣又健康 鐘意釣魚同滑浪<br />\n<br />\n最緊要個人長情 <br />\n除左靜香<br />\n咁多年都係傳過山口智子同松隆子<br />\n山口佢就明戀足廿年  <br />\n（到今時今日一提長假表情都唔同 <br />\n最欣賞女共演永遠都係山口<br />\n想睇木村怕羞就睇山口2次上Smap xSmap)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n傳說松隆子就神女有心 但係木村無意<br />\n不過有好多綜藝都feel到松隆子對木村係特別d<br />\n<br />\n做野又認真<br />\n記對白記埋對手台詞<br />\n演技越來越好<br />\n華麗一族同change<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02ed3f4f83382b4fd104089a009ce0a875d435d","tid":28291,"uid":22643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"771463b8373abd5cbe48d87569d178068fe4c4ba","tid":28291,"uid":56993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:50:59.000Z","msg":"華麗一族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4595f5b833d0a773ddc94dc193e5e615cae220d5","tid":28291,"uid":22643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T00:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>華麗一族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後喊到我死"},{"pid":"ec6fc538139d753dcc27bb4fc9dc2bcbf41a36e7","tid":28291,"uid":56993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:03:03.000Z","msg":"逢木村劇既配樂真係好正<img src=\"/asse